<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Event Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #fffbe6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .reminder {
      background-color: #fdf2c5;
      border: 3px dashed #f39c12;
      border-radius: 15px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #e67e22;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .info {
      margin: 6px 0;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .organizer,
    .attendee {
      margin-top: 20px;
      background-color: #fff9e6;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .reminder-note {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      background-color: #fcf8e3;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 1px dashed #f1c40f;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="reminder">
    <div class="logo">üì£ 24-Hour Reminder from<br><span style="color:#e74c3c;">The Event Management Team</span></div>

    <div class="section-title">{{eventTitle}}</div>
    <div class="info"><em>is happening in less than 24 hours!</em></div>
    <div class="info">üìÖ Date: {{eventDate}}</div>
    <div class="info">‚è∞ Start Time: {{eventStartTime}}</div>
    <div class="info">üìç Venue: {{eventVenue}}</div>

    <div class="organizer">
      <strong>Organizer</strong><br>
      Name: {{organizerName}}<br>
    </div>

    <div class="attendee">
      <strong>Attendee</strong><br>
      Name: {{userName}}<br>
    </div>

    <div class="reminder-note">
      Please make sure to be on time and 
      If you have any questions,<br>
      feel free to reach out to the organizer,<br>
      <strong>{{organizerName}}</strong> via the chat button provided.
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      This is an automated reminder from The Event Management Team.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
